---
import ImageFrame from './ImageFrame.astro';
---
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="badge">Before / After Proof</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Transformation-focused visuals with clear placeholders.</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">These are premium placeholder slots, intentionally styled for this demo. Replace with approved Hydroseed Inc. project photos before launch.</p>
    <div class="cards-2" style="margin-top:1rem;">
      <ImageFrame src="/images/before-lawn-1.svg" alt="Placeholder before image of bare dirt new construction lot in South Bend" caption="Before: Bare post-construction lot" />
      <ImageFrame src="/images/after-lawn-1.svg" alt="Placeholder after image showing established lawn after hydroseeding" caption="After: Healthy early-stage turf establishment" />
      <ImageFrame src="/images/before-lawn-2.svg" alt="Placeholder before image of erosion-prone commercial slope" caption="Before: Erosion-prone slope" />
      <ImageFrame src="/images/after-lawn-2.svg" alt="Placeholder after image of stabilized commercial seeded slope" caption="After: Stabilized seeded coverage" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
